org.gvsig.symbology.fmap.mapcontext.rendering.symbol.fill

Interface IFillSymbol

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CartographicSupport, Cloneable, IPrintable, ISymbol, Persistent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IChartSymbol, IMarkerFillSymbol, IMultiChartSymbol, IMultiLayerFillSymbol, IPictureFillSymbol, ISimpleFillSymbol
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFillSymbol, ChartSymbol, LinkedChartSymbol, MarkerFillSymbol, MultiLayerFillSymbol, MultiShapeSymbol, PictureFillSymbol, SimpleFillSymbol, WarningSymbol

    public interface IFillSymbol
extends ISymbol, CartographicSupport
    Interface that extends ISymbol interface in order to define methods for fill symbols which can manage specific attributes of them.
